  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6802664/" class="title-link">原著比电视剧更好看</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6802664"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/69223544/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u69223544-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/69223544/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">笑满</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-08-06"
      class="main-meta">2014-08-06 14:51:03</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6802664_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《血族》原著本身就比较有画面感，好像是有一个评语说是“小说写得如同电影”，这就是导演的写作功力，不同的线索与人物一个个汇聚又一个个分开。 其实正面描写并不多，但是烘托出来紧张窒息的感觉就很带感！ 私以为比电视剧更好看~

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6802664/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
